119753216?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">很糟糕</a>”，并回复道：“我确信这些脏话也适用于你的电脑。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/team-reptile">Team Reptile</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bomb-rush-cyberfunk"><em>《Bomb Rush Cyber​​funk》</em></a>将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/jet-set-radio-inspired-bomb-rush-cyberfunk-comes-to-consoles-in-september-3476262">9 月</a>登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation">PlayStation</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox">Xbox</a>游戏机，距离 PC 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">Switch</a>发布几周后。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tekken-8-players-have-been-banned-for-illegally-accessing-the-beta-3476301">《铁拳 8》玩家因非法访问测试版将被禁止的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
