_mattbellamy_matthealy_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_mattbellamy_matthealy_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_mattbellamy_matthealy_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_mattbellamy_matthealy_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_mattbellamy_matthealy_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muse">Muse</a>透露了为什么他们在最近的马来西亚演唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/muse-remove-song-malaysia-concert-setlist-the-1975-controversy-3474835">会上交换了歌单中的一首歌曲</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/reviews/album/muse-will-of-the-people-review-3297994">缪斯 - “人民的意志”评论：现代焦虑，以及他们多年来最好的音乐</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，由于主唱 Matty Healy 在舞台上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-good-vibes-festival-malaysia-set-cut-short-matty-healy-criticises-anti-lgbtq-laws-kiss-bassist-3471738">批评马来西亚政府的反 LGBTQ+ 法律，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healy-3471893">The 1975 被禁止在吉隆坡演出，</a>乐队因此更改了歌单。</p><p> Muse 是自事件发生以来，周六（7 月 29 日）在马来西亚演出的第一支大型国际乐队，据吉隆坡演唱会的组织者称，乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/muse-remove-song-malaysia-concert-setlist-the-1975-controversy-3474835">积极确保他们的表演符合该国的指导方针</a>。</p><p> “事件传遍全球后不久，他们就给我们打电话。经过讨论，他们决定根据歌名将其中一首歌曲从歌单中删除。很高兴知道他们渴望娱乐，同时也尊重准则。”Hello Universe 创始人 Adam Ashraf 说道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvX7f0Yo2Qc/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-c